{"tid":1825581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【餅女茶聚】楊愛瑾懷念舊時光 鄧麗欣讚Serena女兒可愛","createTime":"2020-01-15T11:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T21:20:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee799b4b42fcf66c9db89b81b2c502f90f0218c0","tid":1825581,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"於2002年出道，曾經有9位成員的女子組合Cookies，一度是樂壇焦點，亦是唱片公司力捧對象，但組合最後由9變4，只餘鄧麗欣（Stephy）、傅穎（Theresa）、吳雨霏（Kary）及楊愛瑾（Miki），後來隨着各人有自己發展及有成員鬧不和，組合正式解體。不過，除了一直與Stephy鬧不和的Theresa，多位前組合成員亦一直有保持聯絡，昨日5位前「餅女」更相約飯聚，提早團年。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚Miki、Stephy及區文詩（Angela）分別在社交網貼出聚餐合照，當中除了3人及昔日唱片公司戰友，還有甚少露面、早已離開娛樂圈的蒲茜兒（Serena）及陳素瑩（Gloria）；2011年已嫁任職銀行老公Bin的Serena，更帶同兩位可愛女兒出席跟幾位「姨姨」見面。<br />\n<br />\nStephy貼相後留言︰「感謝劇組突如其來的假期，讓我有時間出來跟大家相聚一刻，太難得的一個下午。大家都有一陣子沒有見了，而我覺得&hellip;大家都沒甚麼變化。」她又大讚Serena囡囡又可愛又乖，表示希望下次可以再齊人一點。Miki則寫道：「原來一眨眼我們已經認識18年了，突然好懷念我們那一年的時光，我們的專用巴士，我們的宿舍，每天零晨五點起牀化妝整頭，每天不停的食，最後我肥了二十磅，這一年真的很特別。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579063024_21e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579063024_21e1.jpg&h=f1b1b6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200115/HGUWUK2XL6N5QLFB6J73SX6QTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2FHGUWUK2XL6N5QLFB6J73SX6QTM%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ca95f886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2FHGUWUK2XL6N5QLFB6J73SX6QTM%2F&h=fb7118bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200115/HGUWUK2XL6N5QLFB6J73SX6QTM/</a>"},{"pid":"08865ffa0729ca3261f0601fac8f50c690a71415","tid":1825581,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36080ec74647484f7f3da2f63a06d5d8b31195f","tid":1825581,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"老女人"},{"pid":"e57e6ef7bbf579da1aa505eed0c5c2724ebd066b","tid":1825581,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"蒲茜兒咁鬼似智孝嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"2dc444ab772baea57fa96b63629945a6c4b86269","tid":1825581,"uid":137451,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"區文詩真係好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b41a766f20488221685ee0727656c96118abb52","tid":1825581,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"油不是八十年代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97aa09c2dc6897d4e09a21cd767d8a3376e11f2b","tid":1825581,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"頂 連佢地都成熟 開始覺得自己真係好撚老"},{"pid":"d3a48e0dad6585db955f6329f9a6859d30c6a5ab","tid":1825581,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"感覺最開心都係嫁左同有仔女個個"},{"pid":"1eea7edd54f29e60ad70dfcb0811ea7e24719dc9","tid":1825581,"uid":55679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e57e6ef7bbf579da1aa505eed0c5c2724ebd066b","tid":1825581,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"蒲茜兒咁鬼似智孝嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驗眼啦屌"},{"pid":"e8a0eda71bbcc3a14f60a05158bc5d10e2b92226","tid":1825581,"ui